{"tid":1616601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警局被持刀漢闖入施襲　據報四名警員死亡","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:21:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"636033ea6b02cdfd3048cf1e39a255a907ea86f1","tid":1616601,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎警察總局被一名持刀男人闖入施襲，消息說，四名警員死亡，這名男子其後被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，行兇男子是警局的員工，但未知工種。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四下午約一時，警局事後被封鎖，多部緊急車輛停在外面，警局旁邊的一個地鐵站亦關閉。<br />\n<br />\n原定今日訪問土耳其的內政部長卡斯塔內押後行程，趕到警局視察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7c0742d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&h=23a72608\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"23261f8ba320bce3ef84145559279edde5c0b8c6","tid":1616601,"uid":131264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636033ea6b02cdfd3048cf1e39a255a907ea86f1","tid":1616601,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎警察總局被一名持刀男人闖入施襲，消息說，四名警員死亡，這名男子其後被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，行兇男子是警局的員工，但未知工種。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四下午約一時，警局事後被封鎖，多部緊急車輛停在外面，警局旁邊的一個地鐵站亦關閉。<br />\n<br />\n原定今日訪問土耳其的內政部長卡斯塔內押後行程，趕到警局視察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7c0742d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&h=23a72608\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/comp